{"tid":2030523,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"最後一口嘅香煙喺個窗邊慢慢消失","createTime":"2020-05-22T20:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T21:11:05.000Z","uid":431,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f0581c86ec60640217961396d32fbefe46bb3ea","tid":2030523,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"佢最希望係播住最愛嘅唱片就這樣停止呼吸<br />\n就這樣消極 晴天霹靂<br />\n生命入面嘅平衡就早已消聲匿跡<br />\n就好似摩天大廈都早已變成瓦礫<br />\n佢只希望可以搵到希望 喺個罅隙<br />\n太多壓力壓逼 心裏面太壓抑<br />\n心愈係想去發力愈係打撠<br />\n係解唔開嘅結 逃唔過嘅劫<br />\n神來之筆幫唔到我寫上新一頁 根本無分別<br />\n面上嘅笑容總係帶點勉強<br />\n面上嘅皺紋總係話俾我知佢幾堅強<br />\n仇敵有幾咁無恥卑劣習慣順手牽羊<br />\n佢仍然知道邊條道路通往地獄 天堂喺天上"},{"pid":"4f75d6bb130575f664b7f27b536a3361f4518133","tid":2030523,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3490731a10e8485cd35035c3dac077c6a8d4531","tid":2030523,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f75d6bb130575f664b7f27b536a3361f4518133","tid":2030523,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:16:01.000Z","msg":".牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690e8ab8867f9739e02339ab4980c73886575293","tid":2030523,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3490731a10e8485cd35035c3dac077c6a8d4531","tid":2030523,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f75d6bb130575f664b7f27b536a3361f4518133","tid":2030523,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:16:01.000Z","msg":".牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T20:54:49.000Z","msg":"想聽